I agree that at the time of admission I will be at least 18 years old and I am aware that the application allows only one-time registration. Each participant has only one opportunity to pass the piscine, so it is important to approach this event seriously and with full focus. During the piscine, I understand that I must dedicate enough time each week to school, as it is an intensive learning period requiring full immersion in programming. It will be difficult to combine study or work during this time, so I acknowledge the need for full commitment and ensuring that I am free from other responsibilities. I confirm that my last name and first name are written in English as per my passport. After successfully passing the piscine, my full-time education at Tomorrow School will be scheduled by its administration. I also accept that my personal data will be processed and used accordingly.
